TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
What do you know about the tower?
How do I get around this place?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Of course, I knew you were important right away.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 물론, 처음부터 네가 중요한 인물이란 걸 알았지.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Yeah, me knew you big and important whole time.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 응, 나 처음부터 네가 크고 중요한 거 알았어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Flirt]</Start> Of course you're important... you're so big and strong.
Text: <StartCheck>[유혹]</Start> 물론 넌 중요하지... 그렇게 크고 강하잖아.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Flirt]</Start> Of course you important. You is so big and strong...
Text: <StartCheck>[유혹]</Start> 물론 너 중요해. 너 엄청 크고 힘세잖아...

TextEng: You'll answer my questions now, orc!
You answer questions, orc, or you pay!
Text: 질문 대답해, 오크, 안 그러면 대가 치러!

TextEng: What did you say about the wizards?
Tell me about the Arcane Brotherhood.
What has been happening in the tower?
The new Archmage Arcane? What happened to the old one?
Text: 새 비전 대마법사? 전임은 어떻게 됐어?

TextEng: New wizard leader? What happen to old one?
Text: 새 마법사 우두머리? 옛날 놈 어떻게 됐어?

TextEng: What does he want, do you know?
Let me ask you something else.
You think the orcs will agree?
But what do the wizards need you for?
Text: 근데 마법사들이 널 왜 필요로 해?

TextEng: Okay, that's it. Now you die.
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Oh, I doubt you know anything, then, being an underling...
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 아, 그럼 넌 아무것도 모르겠네, 부하 주제에...

TextEng: Why you has big golem guy?
Why do you have a golem here?
Do you know anything about a cult here?
Have you heard of anyone named Maugrim?
You trusts traitor to lead army, huh?
You trust a traitor to lead the army?
How do you know that's true?
Who this Obould you keeps talking 'bout?
Who is this Obould you keep mentioning?
I am the ambassador from Mulhorand.
